<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Carousel Generator | Script Boxes</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Italiana&display=swap');

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    /* Exact from ContentPage.css .content-page */
    body {
      font-family: 'Italiana', serif;
      background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #d4af37, #e0b841, #f5d76e, #e0b841);
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #1a1410;
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    /* Exact from IncreaseRevenue.js / ContentPage.css .grid-item: card background, border-radius, no box-shadow on default */
    .carousel-box {
      width: 1080px;
      height: 1080px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 80px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: 12px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
    }

    .carousel-box-inner {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 0;
    }

    /* Text block: fills remaining space, centered; font-size set by JS */
    .carousel-box-text {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 0;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0 16px;
    }

    .carousel-box-text p {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1410;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin: 0 0 0.4em 0;
    }

    .carousel-box-text p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    /* Exact from ContentPage.css .icon-container; icon at top-center with consistent padding */
    .carousel-box-icon {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(224, 184, 65, 0.1), rgba(224, 184, 65, 0.2));
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #5D4A1F;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .carousel-box-icon svg {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
    }

    .script-divider {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 48px 0 24px 0;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      background: rgba(26, 20, 16, 0.9);
      color: #e0b841;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border-left: 4px solid #e0b841;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .script-divider:first-of-type {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .box-wrapper {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .download-btn {
      display: block;
      width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto 32px auto;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1410;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0b841, #d4af37);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: inherit;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(224, 184, 65, 0.3);
    }

    .download-btn:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e5c860, #e0b841);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(224, 184, 65, 0.4);
    }

    .section {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="root"></div>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/html2canvas/1.4.1/html2canvas.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    (function() {
      var scripts = [
        {
          title: 'Script 1 — When Leisure Was Invented',
          boxes: [
            "Leisure didn't always exist. People once worked to survive, not relax.",
            "Disposable income became mainstream. The middle class expanded. Time off became cultural.",
            "People started paying for experience.",
            "Restaurants, hotels, venues — they weren't products. They were access to the good life.",
            "Hospitality was built on one idea: life should be enjoyed, not just endured.",
            "We exist because people finally had time and money to enjoy life."
          ]
        },
        {
          title: 'Script 2 — The Golden Era of Experience',
          boxes: [
            "Hospitality once competed on experiences — not speed, cost-cutting, or efficiency.",
            "Operators obsessed over ambience, service standards, and details that guests would remember.",
            "They understood something simple: the product wasn't the meal or the room.",
            "It was how someone felt while they were there.",
            "Experience built loyalty before loyalty programs existed. Memories drove repeat visits.",
            "Somewhere along the way, we started measuring everything — except the experience."
          ]
        },
        {
          title: 'Script 3 — When Efficiency Replaced Experience',
          boxes: [
            "Margins tightened. Scale became the goal. Efficiency became the strategy.",
            "Guests became covers. Staff became labor. Moments became transactions.",
            "Efficiency matters — but when throughput replaces experience, something breaks.",
            "Lines grow longer. Waits become normal. Stress becomes constant.",
            "Your team absorbs that pressure. They're not serving guests — they're fighting friction.",
            "Optimization without empathy creates invisible damage. And eventually — burnout."
          ]
        },
        {
          title: 'Script 4 — Friction Is the Silent memories Killer',
          boxes: [
            "People don't remember the menu. They remember how it felt.",
            "Friction leaves residue — long lines, confusion, chaotic lobbies, and delayed service.",
            "Even if the product is great, friction contaminates the memories.",
            "Friction steals emotional bandwidth — and emotional bandwidth is what you sell.",
            "Great branding and great products mean nothing; if the process feels stressful or confusing.",
            "Flow design is memories design. Reduce friction and the experience improves automatically."
          ]
        },
        {
          title: 'Script 5 — The Profit Equation Everyone Misses',
          boxes: [
            "Better experiences create better memories. Better memories create repeat visits.",
            "Repeat visits increase lifetime value. Lifetime value drives predictable profit.",
            "You don't grow this industry by squeezing labor. You grow it by engineering moments.",
            "When the process is frictionless, the experience becomes effortless. Guests come back.",
            "Hospitality doesn't need reinvention. It needs to be retrofit.",
            "When you design for experiences. Profit follows."
          ]
        }
      ];

      function escapeHtml(text) {
        var div = document.createElement('div');
        div.textContent = text;
        return div.innerHTML;
      }

      /* Lucide icons: clock, star, trending-down, zap, bar-chart (24x24, stroke 2, match IncreaseRevenue icon style) */
      var iconSvgs = [
        '<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>',
        '<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>',
        '<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 17 13.5 8.5 8.5 13.5 2 6"/><polyline points="16 17 22 17 22 11"/></svg>',
        '<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>',
        '<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="10"/><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="16"/></svg>'
      ];

      var root = document.getElementById('root');

      scripts.forEach(function(script, scriptIdx) {
        var divider = document.createElement('div');
        divider.className = 'script-divider';
        divider.textContent = script.title;
        root.appendChild(divider);

        script.boxes.forEach(function(boxText, boxIdx) {
          var section = document.createElement('div');
          section.className = 'section';

          var boxWrapper = document.createElement('div');
          boxWrapper.className = 'box-wrapper';

          var box = document.createElement('div');
          box.className = 'carousel-box';
          box.setAttribute('data-capture', 'true');

          var inner = document.createElement('div');
          inner.className = 'carousel-box-inner';
          var iconWrap = document.createElement('div');
          iconWrap.className = 'carousel-box-icon';
          iconWrap.innerHTML = iconSvgs[scriptIdx];
          inner.appendChild(iconWrap);
          var lines = boxText.split(' / ').map(function(s) { return s.trim(); });
          var textWrap = document.createElement('div');
          textWrap.className = 'carousel-box-text';
          lines.forEach(function(line) {
            var p = document.createElement('p');
            p.textContent = line;
            textWrap.appendChild(p);
          });
          /* Dynamic font size: fit all lines in box without clipping (box 1080px, padding 80, icon ~84px) */
          var textAreaHeight = 1080 - 160 - 84;
          var lineCount = lines.length;
          var fontSize = Math.min(72, Math.max(28, Math.floor(textAreaHeight / (lineCount * 1.3))));
          textWrap.style.fontSize = fontSize + 'px';
          inner.appendChild(textWrap);

          box.appendChild(inner);
          boxWrapper.appendChild(box);

          var btn = document.createElement('button');
          btn.type = 'button';
          btn.className = 'download-btn';
          var defaultBtnText = 'Download PNG';
          btn.textContent = defaultBtnText;
          btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
            btn.disabled = true;
            btn.textContent = 'Generating PNG...';

            var btnOriginalDisplay = btn.style.display;
            btn.style.display = 'none';

            html2canvas(box, {
              scale: 1,
              useCORS: true,
              logging: false,
              backgroundColor: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25)'
            }).then(function(canvas) {
              btn.style.display = btnOriginalDisplay;
              btn.disabled = false;
              btn.textContent = defaultBtnText;

              var imgData = canvas.toDataURL('image/png');
              var link = document.createElement('a');
              link.download = 'script-' + (scriptIdx + 1) + '-box-' + (boxIdx + 1) + '.png';
              link.href = imgData;
              link.click();
            }).catch(function(err) {
              btn.style.display = btnOriginalDisplay;
              btn.disabled = false;
              btn.textContent = defaultBtnText;
              console.error('PNG generation failed:', err);
            });
          });

          section.appendChild(boxWrapper);
          section.appendChild(btn);
          root.appendChild(section);
        });
      });
    })();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
